categories: Category:Imperial Navy captains of the Galactic Empire

nodes.text: A human male Imperial officer served as a captain aboard Transport 651. His ship was boarded by rebels in order to rescue Wookiee slaves, although it was a trap set by Agent Kallus. The ship was captured by Kallus' Star Destroyer. The officer greeted Kallus when he came aboard, and later joined Kallus on the Star Destroyer after the rebels destroyed the freighter.
The officer appears in the 2014 film Star Wars Rebels: Spark of Rebellion.
